snippet.title: Temperia: Soul of Majestic - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Temperia: Soul of Majestic is a competitive card-based board game. Quick, strategic and totally open-handed, every match is different from others thanks to the abilities of the creatures, the equipment, the powers and the elemental spaces presented in the board.
